M|Coho|tx|\| Feb 2024 \| 100% \| 94% \| 90% \| 87% \| 80% \|
M|Coho|tx|\| Mar 2024 \| 100% \| 92% \| 86% \| 82% \| - \|
M|Coho|**Qu|**
M|Coho|it|Are recent cohorts retaining better or worse than older cohorts?
M|Coho|- If|pd-mk fit is degrading (fix before scaling)
M|Coho|- If|Improvements are working (safe to scale)
M|Coho|it|Track rv retention by cohort, not just logo retention
