M|Exam|**Re|**
M|Exam|- MR|$2M (growing 10% month-over-month)
M|Exam|- AR|$24M
M|Exam|- AR|$1,200/month (200 accounts)
M|Exam|- AR|$120/month (20,000 us)
M|Exam|- Av|100 per account
M|Exam|**Re|**
M|Exam|- Mo|2%
M|Exam|- Re|1.5% (losing smaller cs)
M|Exam|- NR|115% (strong expansion)
M|Exam|- Ex|$200K/month (10% of MRR)
M|Exam|- Qu|5.0
M|Exam|al|**
M|Exam|it|✅ Strong growth (10% MoM MRR)
M|Exam|it|✅ Excellent retention (2% logo churn, 115% NRR)
M|Exam|it|✅ Healthy expansion (NRR >100%)
M|Exam|it|✅ Sustainable (Quick Ratio 5.0)
